**outfitfor.me**
------------

An app that will suggest a good clothing combination based on the weather.

Github repo: https://github.com/codedoll/outfitforme
Waffle link: https://waffle.io/codedoll/outfitforme

User Stories
-------------
 - User must be able to sign up
 - User must be able to sign in after signing up
 - User must be able to change his/her password
 - User must be able to change his/her email
 - When a user inputs a zipcode, it should display the weather for that day
 - User will get a recommendation based on the weather that day


